         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2190, recto: (1) Semmonthis, the wife of Peteminis, son of Userhape, has paid (2) 1/4 silver for salt silver of year 27. Signed, Psemminis, (3) son of Khered ------, in year 28, [Thoth 5]. (4) (Greek) Year 28, Thoth 5. (5) (Greek) -------.</ab>
